Package gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Menu
    The Menu interface defines a method for setting a welcome message.
    SceneSetter
    The SceneSetter interface defines methods for setting a JavaFX scene and keeping track of the previous screen.
    Testing
    The Testing interface defines a method for handling the case when a test is manually locked by a lecturer.
    Tests
    The Tests interface defines methods for accessing test-related information in the GUI.
